go with that one.

00:01:12.530 --> 00:01:15.283 position:50% align:center
I'm starting to think
you're a fudanshi, too.

00:01:15.367 --> 00:01:18.912 position:50% align:center
[KURESAWA] No. I'm just an
extremely dedicated boyfriend.

00:02:49.544 --> 00:02:51.963 position:50% align:center
[HANZAWA]
Good to see you, old friend.

00:02:52.047 --> 00:02:53.757 position:50% align:center
Do you like my getup?

00:02:53.840 --> 00:02:55.175 position:50% align:center
Yeah, it looks great.

00:02:55.258 --> 00:02:56.259 position:50% align:center
