00:02:56.343 --> 00:02:58.261 position:50% align:center
the cafe's delinquent
theme, though.

00:02:58.345 --> 00:02:59.512 position:50% align:center
Well, I tried to do that,

00:02:59.596 --> 00:03:01.431 position:50% align:center
