00:03:03.433 --> 00:03:05.727 position:50% align:center
[MIYANO] I'd ask, but I'm
not sure I want to know.

00:03:05.810 --> 00:03:08.772 position:50% align:center
I always thought I had
such a friendly face.

00:03:08.855 --> 00:03:12.150 position:50% align:center
[MIYANO] That mask is making him
look anything but friendly.

00:03:12.233 --> 00:03:13.401 position:50% align:center
Now, Miyano.

00:03:13.485 --> 00:03:15.070 position:50% align:center
Tell me about a problem
you're struggling with,

00:03:15.153 --> 00:03:17.822 position:50% align:center
and I'll use the tarot
to help you solve it.

00:03:17.906 --> 00:03:20.283 position:50% align:center
[MIYANO] Is the crystal ball
just for looks?

00:03:20.367 --> 00:03:21.701 position:50% align:center
[HANZAWA] We even
designed this custom deck

00:03:21.785 --> 00:03:23.161 position:50% align:center
to fit the delinquent theme!

00:03:23.244 --> 00:03:24.954 position:50% align:center
No detail is too small!

00:03:25.038 --> 00:03:27.374 position:50% align:center
[MIYANO] They really
thought of everything!

00:03:27.457 --> 00:03:30.418 position:50% align:center
Has anything been weighing
on your mind recently?

00:03:30.502 --> 00:03:33.421 position:50% align:center
Like, for instance, how to
land a date with your crush?

00:03:33.505 --> 00:03:34.964 position:50% align:center
Or where you should
go on said date

00:03:35.048 --> 00:03:36.883 position:50% align:center
to confess your
undying devotion?

00:03:36.966 --> 00:03:37.967 position:50% align:center
Perhaps you'd like to know

00:03:38.051 --> 00:03:39.302 position:50% align:center
how your sweetheart
feels about you?

00:03:39.386 --> 00:03:41.554 position:50% align:center
The more specific
you are, the better.

00:03:41.638 --> 00:03:44.057 position:50% align:center
Is it me, or do all those things
have to do with love?

00:03:44.140 --> 00:03:46.810 position:50% align:center
Such are the dilemmas
of our youth.

00:03:46.893 --> 00:03:48.436 position:50% align:center
Right.

00:03:48.520 --> 00:03:49.771 position:50% align:center
Aw, don't be shy!

00:03:49.854 --> 00:03:51.773 position:50% align:center
Pretend I'm a random
fortune teller on the street

00:03:51.856 --> 00:03:53.900 position:50% align:center
and tell me your deepest,
darkest secrets.

00:03:53.983 --> 00:03:55.568 position:50% align:center
