I'll be right with you.

00:06:42.986 --> 00:06:44.738 position:50% align:center
Sure. No prob.

00:06:44.821 --> 00:06:46.740 position:50% align:center
[HANZAWA] I thought
he had ten more minutes.

00:06:46.823 --> 00:06:48.366 position:50% align:center
